title: Man life totally sucks when you have a job/busy all the time
body:
I have to choose between playing League, being an artist, working out, hanging out with friends, and like everything else.  I have like no free time anymore and I feel like I'm never going to have free time until I'm retired.  I'm only 20 yet it's like my life is already over.

>ROFL no I mean like out of the small free time that I have, I have to choose what to do.  I can't do them all even though I want to :C
